  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p698689/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201409/30c544e7499d495687146045ccf9ab9d.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tIt can be very frustrating when a pizza you&rsquo;ve ordered isn&rsquo;t delivered on time.你点的披萨要是不能按时到，那可真够糟糕的。</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">That said, given many drivers deliver their food on motorbikes, there&rsquo;s one good excuse for turning up late, or not at all: being in a road accident.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">考虑到许多送货员骑摩托车送餐，车祸是迟到或不到的不错理由。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Over in Portland, Oregon, this was the&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/fate\" target=\"_blank\">fate</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;that&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/befell\" target=\"_blank\">befell</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;a Pizza Hut worker as he made his way to hand over some cheesy goodness to a customer.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">俄勒冈州波特兰市的一名必胜客员工就在送餐途中遭遇车祸。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">But to ensure his efforts didn&rsquo;t go to waste, two police officers decided to finish the job on his behalf &ndash; and since, a picture proving their valiant efforts has been circulating on Reddit.</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">为了不让他的努力白费，两名警官决定接过他的工作。一张足以说明警官们辛勤工作的照片在红迪网上传播开来。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&lsquo;Community policing at its finest!&rsquo;, the&nbsp;</span><a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/contented\" target=\"_blank\">contented</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;user said. </span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">心满意足的点餐者说：</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp;&ldquo;社区警察太棒了！&rdquo;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"></span></p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p698689/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p698689\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p698559/\">《唐顿庄园》第五季开播 人物12年不老被吐槽</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p698542/\">加拿大女飞贼 获评世界最性感罪犯</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p667116/\">10招提升自信：你不知道自己有多棒！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p657382/\">又涨姿势了：9幅象形图诠释男女差异</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p698536/\">40米深的喜悦：世界最深游泳池开放</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p159334/\">超萌爱心盒饭大比拼：不仅仅是美食</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p672013/\">职场女神：高效女性的七大习惯</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p532552/\">免费在线学：CCTalk英语大厅课程表</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p698361/\">又到金秋结婚季 最受欢迎婚礼大盘点</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"ht